---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Over nise.nl"
	description="nise.nl bouwt handgemaakte websites voor het MKB. Geen grote bureaus, geen standaardoplossingen — persoonlijk contact en kwaliteit die je terugziet."
>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!--                   Banner                     -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<div id="banner-843">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <span class="cs-int-title">Over ons</span>
    </div>
    <picture class="cs-background" aria-hidden="true">
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images%2FPeople%2Fyoga-m.jpg">
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images%2FPeople%2Fyoga.jpg">
        <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images%2FPeople%2Fyoga.jpg" alt="kantoor" width="1280" height="568">
    </picture>
    <svg class="cs-wave" width="1920" height="179" viewBox="0 0 1920 179" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M1920 179V91.3463C1835.33 91.3463 1715.47 76.615 1549.2 32.9521C1299.48 -32.3214 1132.77 12.1006 947.32 61.5167C810.762 97.9044 664.042 137 466.533 137C331.607 137 256.468 123.447 188.082 111.113C130.974 100.812 78.5746 91.3609 0 91.3609V179H1920Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
</div>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!--                 Side By Side                 -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<section id="sbs-about">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <div class="cs-image-group">
            <picture class="cs-background">
                <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images/People/people10.jpg">
                <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images/People/people10.jpg">
                <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images/People/people10.jpg" alt="team nise.nl" width="605" height="690">
            </picture>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-content">
            <span class="cs-topper">nise.nl</span>
            <h2 class="cs-title">Een menselijke aanpak voor digitale marketing</h2>

            <p class="cs-text">
                Wij zijn nise.nl — een webbureau met één duidelijk doel: kleine en middelgrote bedrijven een professionele online aanwezigheid geven die ze verdienen.
            </p>
            <p class="cs-text">
                Na jaren te hebben gewerkt voor grote corporates en enterprise-omgevingen, zagen we een patroon: het MKB werd steeds vaker behandeld als een bijzaak. Standaard templates, dure contracten en weinig persoonlijk contact. Dat kon beter.
            </p>
            <p class="cs-text">
                Echter besloten wij het anders te doen. Geen grote bureaus met accountmanagers die je naam niet kennen. Wij werken direct met je samen. Jij belt ons. Wij nemen op.
            </p>
            <p class="cs-text">
                Daarom bieden wij een pakket aan vanaf €0 aanbetaling en €150 per maand. Want elke ondernemer verdient een website die werkt — ongeacht het budget.
            </p>

            <a href="/contact/" class="cs-button-solid">Kom kennismaken</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!--               Waarom nise.nl                 -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<section id="about-values">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <div class="cs-content">
            <span class="cs-topper">Onze aanpak</span>
            <h2 class="cs-title">Wat ons anders maakt</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="cs-card-group">
            <li class="cs-item">
                <h3 class="cs-h3">
                    <img class="cs-h3-icon" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Icons/trophy.svg" alt="icoon" width="32" height="32">
                    Handgemaakte code
                </h3>
                <p class="cs-item-text">
                    Elke website bouwen wij van de grond af aan. Geen WordPress, geen page builder, geen overbodige code. Het resultaat: razendsnel en robuust.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <h3 class="cs-h3">
                    <img class="cs-h3-icon" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Icons/circle-check.svg" alt="icoon" width="32" height="32">
                    Geld-terug-garantie
                </h3>
                <p class="cs-item-text">
                    Kunnen we geen design maken waar jij volledig tevreden over bent? Dan krijg je je geld terug. We zetten onze naam alleen onder werk waar we trots op zijn.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <h3 class="cs-h3">
                    <img class="cs-h3-icon" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Icons/trophy.svg" alt="icoon" width="32" height="32">
                    Directe ondersteuning
                </h3>
                <p class="cs-item-text">
                    Bel of mail ons elke werkdag. Je krijgt ons direct aan de lijn — geen ticketsysteem, geen wachtrij, geen robots.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <h3 class="cs-h3">
                    <img class="cs-h3-icon" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Icons/circle-check.svg" alt="icoon" width="32" height="32">
                    Jarenlange expertise
                </h3>
                <p class="cs-item-text">
                    Ons team heeft uitgebreide ervaring in webdevelopment — voor zowel kleine zelfstandigen als grote ondernemingen. Die kennis zetten wij in voor jouw bedrijf.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!--                    CTA                       -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<section id="cta-about">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <div class="cs-content">
            <span class="cs-topper">Klaar om te starten?</span>
            <h2 class="cs-title">Laten we iets moois maken</h2>
            <p class="cs-text">
                Geen verkooppraatje. Geen verplichtingen. Gewoon een eerlijk gesprek over wat jij nodig hebt en of wij de juiste partner zijn.
            </p>
            <a class="cs-button-solid" href="/contact/">Neem contact op</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style lang="less">

/*-- -------------------------- -->
<---          Banner            -->
<--- -------------------------- -*/

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    #banner-843 {
        padding: clamp(10.9375rem, 20vw, 16.25rem) (16/16rem) clamp(6.25rem, 14vw, 12vw);
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;

        .cs-container {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: (1280/16rem);
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: (16/16rem);
        }

        .cs-int-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.4375rem, 6.4vw, 3.8125rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.2em;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite);
        }

        .cs-background {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: block;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: -1;

            &:before {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                display: block;
                height: 100%;
                width: 100%;
                background: #1a1a1a;
                opacity: 0.64;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                z-index: 1;
            }

            img {
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                height: 100%;
                width: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
            }
        }

        .cs-wave {
            width: (768/16rem);
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            bottom: -1px;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: -1;
        }
    }
}

@media only screen and (min-width: 48rem) {
    #banner-843 .cs-wave {
        width: 100%;
        left: 0;
        transform: none;
    }
}

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    body.dark-mode #banner-843 .cs-wave path {
        fill: var(--dark);
    }
}

/*-- -------------------------- -->
<---        Side By Side        -->
<--- -------------------------- -*/

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    #sbs-about {
        padding: var(--sectionPadding);

        .cs-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: (1280/16rem);
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        }

        .cs-image-group {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: (586/16rem);
            height: (520/16rem);
            border-radius: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .cs-background {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;

            img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
                display: block;
            }
        }

        .cs-content {
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: (630/16rem);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .cs-text {
            margin-bottom: (16/16rem);
            &:last-of-type {
                margin-bottom: (32/16rem);
            }
        }
    }
}

@media only screen and (min-width: 64rem) {
    #sbs-about .cs-container {
        max-width: (1280/16rem);
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: stretch;
    }

    #sbs-about .cs-image-group {
        height: auto;
    }
}

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    body.dark-mode #sbs-about {
        .cs-topper { color: var(--primary); }
        .cs-title, .cs-text { color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite); }
        .cs-text { opacity: 0.8; }
    }
}

/*-- -------------------------- -->
<---        About Values        -->
<--- -------------------------- -*/

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    #about-values {
        padding: var(--sectionPadding);
        background-color: #f7f7f7;

        .cs-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: (1280/16rem);
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        }

        .cs-content {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .cs-card-group {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(15.625rem, 1fr));
            gap: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
        }

        .cs-item {
            list-style: none;
            padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: (16/16rem);
            border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: (12/16rem);
        }

        .cs-h3 {
            font-size: (20/16rem);
            line-height: 1.2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--headerColor);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: (8/16rem);
        }

        .cs-h3-icon {
            width: (32/16rem);
            height: auto;
        }

        .cs-item-text {
            font-size: (14/16rem);
            line-height: 1.5em;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--bodyTextColor);
        }
    }
}

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    body.dark-mode #about-values {
        background-color: var(--dark);

        .cs-item {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .cs-title, .cs-h3, .cs-item-text { color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite); }
        .cs-item-text { opacity: 0.8; }
    }
}

/*-- -------------------------- -->
<---           CTA              -->
<--- -------------------------- -*/

@media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
    #cta-about {
        padding: var(--sectionPadding);
        background-color: var(--primary);

        .cs-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: (1280/16rem);
            margin: auto;
        }

        .cs-content {
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .cs-topper { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
        .cs-title { color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite); }
        .cs-text {
            color: var(--bodyTextColorWhite);
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: (32/16rem);
        }

        .cs-button-solid {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: var(--primary);

            &:hover {
                background-color: #1a1a1a;
                color: #fff;
            }
        }
    }
}

</style>
